    </Relationships>
    <Content>The robot shall implement an autonomous exploration loop consisting of data acquisition, localisation, mapping, decision making, and motion command generation, repeating until a termination condition is reached (maze fully explored or external stop).</Content>
  </Requirement>

  <Requirement ID="LL-EXPL-1.1.2">
    <Type>FR</Type>
    <Name>Frontier-based Exploration Strategy</Name>
    <Relationships>
      <Refines>HL-EXPL-1.1</Refines>
      <DependsOn>LL-EXPL-1.1.1</DependsOn>
    </Relationships>
    <Content>The robot shall implement frontier-based exploration by selecting adjacent unknown cells, computing a frontier score, and choosing the highest-scoring frontier as the next target; it shall avoid revisiting explored areas and update the exploration loop accordingly.</Content>
  </Requirement>

  <Requirement ID="LL-EXPL-1.1.3">
    <Type>FR</Type>
