  </Requirement>

  <Requirement ID="LL-WALL-1.2.3">
    <Type>FR</Type>
    <Name>Sensor Confirmation for Walls</Name>
    <Relationships>
      <Refines>HL-EXPL-1.2</Refines>
      <DependsOn>LL-WALL-1.2.2</DependsOn>
    </Relationships>
    <Content>The robot shall corroborate wall detections using at least two independent sensors to reduce false positives and maintain confidence in obstacle presence; inconsistent readings shall be handled by re-checking or waiting for additional data.</Content>
  </Requirement>

